Subject: Error message "Invalid Object Name"
Description:
Hey team, how are you?

I'm facing some problems that surely is some tiny detail I'm forgetting about, is it possible you guys help me shed a light on it?

 On several jobs I'm trying to run (mostly SQL related) this error is appearing "Invalid Object Name" followed by some query.  I'm crawling the documentation but no success 'til now, 
What am I missing here, please?

Thank you very much.
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
SQL reports are not running successfully

[Root Cause]
Errors on the SQL Collection jobs

[Resolution]
- Installed the Sensitive Data Discovery add-on to the NEA Console server
- Created a host list that just contained the SQL server “SKYLINE” to run the SQL jobs against
- Kicked off the Database0.CollectionSQL group and began seeing successes
